Mask, commander of the U.S. Air Force Honor Guard at Joint Base Anacostia-Bolling, Washington, D.C., provided the photo on May 30, 2024, and shared how his mother’s perseverance made a positive impact on his life in recognition of Asian American, Native Hawaiian and Pacific Islander Heritage Month.
